{"tid":870209,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"喜馬拉雅兔 Himalayan Rabbit","createTime":"2018-10-21T02:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T03:33:40.000Z","uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1177424e4b6e8ab6c0af3737ecf6634154ab0b6a","tid":870209,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gZntRS0xz9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgZntRS0xz9c&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAeqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=24a38dd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gZntRS0xz9c</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MEw2LfhWZkE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMEw2LfhWZkE&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAeqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=50bc8e91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MEw2LfhWZkE</a>"},{"pid":"8fca503079a2af542430f2175da82f1621111d1e","tid":870209,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:43:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>怎樣叫兔仔回到籠裡？不用抱！</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal), 在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animals)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚。因此，兔子不喜歡被抱來抱去。當牠逃跑的時候，你還去追住抱，會令兔子和主人的信任更差。但如果主人與兔子的關係親密，牠都會喜歡同主人擁抱。以下video可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpyL0yEs-ka8&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAeqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=81afe5b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<br />\n最好的方法去叫牠入籠是每晚(比如：22:00）搖零食樽或pellet 樽幾下，再引牠進入籠吃。幾天後，兔子就會記得零食樽的聲音知道是時候回到籠吃。習慣後，牠會自動22:00左右提主人你是時候回到籠裡吃東西。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 有教：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RJcvi7o4YXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRJcvi7o4YXA&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAeqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=e1a2904a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RJcvi7o4YXA</a>"},{"pid":"fb0093f50967ed283d817ea966a11674d10699f3","tid":870209,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 感人！☺</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAeqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=491fb67b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a>"}]}